Create Role Statement
The create role statement creates an attribute for a specified role identifier. This statement has the following syntax:
create role role_id {, role_id}
[with with_option {, with_option}];

assistant:
The create role statement takes 2 attributes to define a new role in Actian 4GL SQL. These are the name of the role and its password. For example:
create role employee_1 with
    name = 'Mary Smith';
    password = 'secret';
